  "description": "Listed Building Consent application for removal of internal walls upstairs to create open plan kitchen/lounge and installation of upstairs bathroom and associated drainage and ventilation in situ of kitchen. Upgrade to electrics and older gas/water pipework. Replacement of older heating/hot water to modern combi boiler in kitchen and move to new kitchen location and removal of older water tank cupboard above stairwell. Removal of unused chimney breast in current loungeroom with installation of supports for above chimneys. Change of stair rail and surfacing to match new flooring upstairs (with replacement of existing sound proofing on upstairs floor for below) and boxing of under stairs to hide current storage. Below, removal of non structural walls to take use of hallway in main bedroom with removal of unused chimney breast as above. Conversion of current bathroom into a secondary bedroom/office, with hot water tank cupboard removed and conversion of rear half sash half window into a door of similar design out to garden. In rear garden, construction of outbuilding with connected power and 'green roof'.\r\nWritten advice with site visit\t£762.55 \t£152.51\t£915.06",
